AS PASSED SENATE
A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Part 1 of Article 5 of Chapter 9 of Title 45 of the Official Code of Georgia
2 Annotated, relating to Georgia State Indemnification Fund, so as to authorize the Department
3 of Administrative Services to purchase annuities for the payment of indemnification claims;
4 to provide for qualification standards for indemnification claims relating to certain deaths of
5 public safety officers related to COVID-19; to provide for timing requirements for
6 application of such indemnification claims; to provide for definitions; to provide for
7 conforming changes; to provide for related matters; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other
8 purposes.
9 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
10 SECTION 1.
11 Part 1 of Article 5 of Chapter 9 of Title 45 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated,
12 relating to Georgia State Indemnification Fund, is amended by revising Code
13 Section 45-9-85, relating to payment of indemnification for death or disability, procedure for
14 making payments, and appeal, as follows:
15 "45-9-85.
16 (a) As used in this Code section, the term:
